name: CookingTips
0:
”Alexa, open cooking tip”
”Alexa, tell cooking tip to give me a cooking tip”
”Alexa, open cooking tip and tell me about cooking”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cooking tip
des: Learn some new cooking tips to improve your skills in the kitchen! Alexa will tell you about how long to braise pork belly all the way to the best way to remove corn kernels. Simply prompt Alexa by saying "Alexa open cooking tip" and then ask "Give me a cooking fact".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
